title: Nine To Noon - 3/3 Nordo in for PA... Florio, Stump the Snob, Jonny Athletic, Dan Hayes
description: Mike Florio checks in to react to the end-of-an era news that Kyle Rudolph has been released by the Vikes after a decade... We play Stump the Snob, and check in with guests Jonny Athletic and Twins beat writer Dan Hayes of the Athletic!
